/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the scene below. The street, divided by a median, is teeming with cars and buses, indicating a busy time of day. The buildings flanking the street are tall and modern, their glass facades reflecting the overcast sky. The trees lining the street are lush and green, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. The sky above is overcast, casting a soft light over the scene. Despite the busyness of the street, there's a sense of order and rhythm to the scene, a testament to the city's organized chaos.
